window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Pure Empathy (639 Hz)</i></p> <p>639 Hertz is the frequency of love, connection, and pure empathy. This sound meditation enhances your ability to connect with others and deepen relationships. It opens your heart and fosters understanding, making it an excellent choice for anyone looking to cultivate empathy and strengthen their emotional bonds with others.</p> <p>Welcome to a remarkable sonic journey through distinct healing frequencies, each designed to offer therapeutic benefits and unlock your innate potential for holistic well-being.</p> <p>At the heart of sound healing lies the phenomenon of resonance. This occurs when a system vibrates at its natural state in response to an external stimulus of the same frequency. Every part of the human body—organs, tissues, and cells—has its own, unique natural frequency. When we introduce specific sound frequencies to the body, they interact with these natural vibrations, creating a resonance effect that influences us on multiple levels: physical, mental, emotional, and even energetic.</p>"; 
